dct_title_s: Ukraine, Moldova 1:1 100 000 [cartographic material] : geographical map with index, Kiev, L'viv, Crimean Riviera 1:500 000 / Gizi Map (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Wall map of roads and tourist features. Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Depths shown by contours and gradient tints. Title from upper margin at left. "© GIZIMAP Hungary." Includes highway distance table and insets of Lʹviv, Kyiv, and southern Crimea. Indexes of places and key to abbreviations on verso.
